BP Wins U.S. Deep-Water Gulf of Mexico Drilling Plan Approval

-- B y   K a t a r z y n a   K l i m a s i n s k a
-- 
2011-10-21T15:00:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-21/bp-wins-u-s-deep-water-gulf-of-mexico-drilling-plan-approval.html
BP Plc (BP/)  received permission from U.S.
regulators for oil exploration in the deep waters of the  Gulf of
Mexico , the first approval since the company’s Macondo well
caused the nation’s worst offshore spill last year.  The decision was announced in an e-mailed statement from
the Interior Department today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Katarzyna Klimasinska in Washington at 
 kklimasinska@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steve Geimann at 
 sgeimann@bloomberg.net  